{"tid":810336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拉完央視分台記者 肯雅警再拘《中國日報》主管","createTime":"2018-09-08T01:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T15:37:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8eb10291661a351f2ec6c3dbf7e6cd30902d0b","tid":810336,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180907/large/1536329653_f743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180907%2Flarge%2F1536329653_f743.jpg&h=a84dd461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯雅警方繼周三（5日）搜查中國央視在當地分台的辦公室後，今日又再「突擊」《中國日報》（China Daily）駐當地的分社辦公室，一名持有效工作簽證的《中國日報》分社高層職員遭短暫扣留，事件已引起中國駐當地大使館關注。<br />\n<br />\n據南非Eyewitness News報道，肯雅警方進入今日進入位於首都內羅畢的《中國日報》分社後要求檢查職員展示證件，警員經網上查核後確認副主管劉宏杰（音譯，Liu Hongjie）的工作簽證有效，不知何故仍把他帶回警署。<br />\n<br />\n內羅畢警方周三以打擊非法入境者為由，派出荷槍實彈的警員到中國環球電視網非洲分台搜查，並一度扣留13名中國記者。肯雅當局事後指，搜查中國環球電視網非洲分台是一次錯誤行動。中國外交部發言人華春瑩同日指，中國駐肯雅使館獲悉此事後即向肯尼亞高層提出交涉，肯雅已就執法不當向中方表達歉意，並承諾將約束基層警察行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180907/58657752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58657752&d=NcR7R2YgvSmy%2FZlfdaZChQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=4b8bcffe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180907%2F58657752&h=c3b171bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180907/58657752</a>"},{"pid":"ebbeb148201b1877cd955c017b64b43a568f8932","tid":810336,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0d2c45b0826f508de6063221ad09d2e31